{"tid":942171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"感冒還身穿短褲公演 最終倒下的雪炫","createTime":"2018-12-15T12:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T20:07:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea42483155245a186a5c63ff1e9562da0c14944e","tid":942171,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/12/15/700/j1oghran2u33474ae3ak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F12%2F15%2F700%2Fj1oghran2u33474ae3ak.jpg&h=1d715e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女團AOA的成員雪炫在演出中暈倒了。<br />\n<br />\n15日下午，女子組合AOA參加了在首爾安岩高麗大學花亭體育館舉行的&lsquo;port nate korea open舞台活動&rsquo;。<br />\n<br />\n當天AOA在結束人氣歌曲《like a cat》的舞台之後，正在準備下一首歌曲《怦然心動》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/12/15/700/n839i69kjk27xsk4j4h3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F12%2F15%2F700%2Fn839i69kjk27xsk4j4h3.jpg&h=48613bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/12/15/700/uu01t787rf9hsicon99e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F12%2F15%2F700%2Fuu01t787rf9hsicon99e.jpg&h=1c2aac41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但是AOA的成員雪炫坐了一會兒，勉強站了起來，但面色蒼白，氣喘吁吁。<br />\n<br />\n擔心雪炫的成員們一直攙扶著雪炫，但是雪炫卻無法站穩身子，搖搖晃晃站著。<br />\n<br />\n之後雪炫在演出相關人士們陪同下在後台休息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/12/15/700/149h935rs1z6bu1q0isg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F12%2F15%2F700%2F149h935rs1z6bu1q0isg.jpg&h=e8cf034d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一起觀看這一幕的粉絲們也開始驚慌失措。<br />\n<br />\n留在舞台上的AOA成員們表示：&ldquo;雪炫現在因為感冒身體不好，不用擔心。&rdquo;，試圖讓粉絲們安心。<br />\n<br />\n之後AOA在沒有雪炫的情況下結束舞台演出，最後以&ldquo;成員到最後都沒能在一起，對不起&rdquo;結束問候後退場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nF2UdmYSSCI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnF2UdmYSSCI&d=%2FiaVEXIQqIBypw03stmNOnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2162a9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nF2UdmYSSCI</a>"},{"pid":"946f0b301499d527a908e3316e360a2d9d30f584","tid":942171,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761447bce8be81851650565afcefe7a066a167f9","tid":942171,"uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"之前冬運D表演場好似落埋雪手腳紅晒<br />\nD IDOL都要照跳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9865fdfbd7aaad02e5306e66349764ae29a7e853","tid":942171,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761447bce8be81851650565afcefe7a066a167f9","tid":942171,"uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"之前冬運D表演場好似落埋雪手腳紅晒<br />\nD IDOL都要照跳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好敬業"},{"pid":"6dc8b1e5e67d3a114da1